description: This file is a C header file defining the interface for TelcoVoiceManager message bus interactions. It declares function prototypes related to message bus engagement, initialization, finalization, bus checking, and resource freeing.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_MessageBusEngage
methods.description: Engages the message bus for the specified component using the provided configuration file and path.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_Initialize
methods.description: Initializes the message bus interface with user data.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_Finalize
methods.description: Finalizes and cleans up the message bus interface with user data.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_Buscheck
methods.description: Checks the status of the message bus using user data.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_FreeResources
methods.description: Frees resources associated with the message bus with a given priority and user data.
